<!-- Node: "Half-Life Monster's Arrive" -->
<div class="body_box_header">Half-Life Monster's Arrive</div>
<div class="body_box"><small>Submitted by <a href="http://www.gamedesign.net/user/view/2198" title="View user profile.">Andy</a> on Friday, July 16, 2004 - 09:56</small><br /><br />
<p>Consider RUST well and truely <b>Monstered</b>.<br> <i>Umm..Yeah, I know it doesn't have quite the same ring as Func'd</i>...<br>
All 41 of your favorite critters have been added to the<br> Half-Life <a href="http://www.gamedesign.net/book/view/183">Monster Entity Properties</a>.<br>
Check them out and please add a comment, if there is any important information I might have missed. </p>
