<!-- Node: "Another .plan update by Todd Hollenshead" -->
<div class="body_box_header">Another .plan update by Todd Hollenshead</div>
<div class="body_box"><small>Submitted by <a href="http://www.gamedesign.net/user/view/2157" title="View user profile.">method</a> on Thursday, July 15, 2004 - 18:48</small><br /><br />
Todd Hollenshead, Id Software CEO, updated his .plan today. He talks about the Mac and Linux DOOM 3 versions and upcomming DOOM 3 demo, which will be ready by the time DOOM 3 hits the US stores. Here's the <a href = "http://www.webdog.org/plans/6/">.plan</a>.
