<!-- Node: "Doom 3 Gold!" -->
<div class="body_box_header">Doom 3 Gold!</div>
<div class="body_box"><small>Submitted by <a href="http://www.gamedesign.net/user/view/8" title="View user profile.">Jherax</a> on Wednesday, July 14, 2004 - 12:59</small><br /><br />
Todd Hollenshead of id Software updated his .plan file earlier today to let the world know that:
<blockquote>
IT'S DONE!!!!!!!<p>
Yes, this is the official word that DOOM 3 has been code released and has been approved for manufacturing!
</blockquote>
Slated to be on store shelves August 5th, woo.
