<div class="body_box"><small>Submitted by <a href="http://www.gamedesign.net/user/view/2157" title="View user profile.">method</a> on Monday, July 12, 2004 - 05:03</small><br /><br />
I'm working on unofficial sequel to Kingpin, entitled Kingpin: Final Crime. KP:FC will include new maps, cutscenes, characters, voices and story. I haven't set the release date, but KP:FC is almost ready and will be shipped this month.<br><br>

